(1. Removed external EEPROM; will be migrated to ESP32's NVS) Tj
T* (2. Removed in-line interrupt resistors between PCA9555PW's and GPIO; INTs are now direct drive) Tj
T* (3. U3 \(input ports 1-4\) interrupt moved from GPIO35 to GPIO34) Tj
T* (4. U4 \(input ports 5-8\) interrupt moved from GPIO25 to GPIO35) Tj
T* (5. U6 moved from GPIO27 to GPIO33) Tj
T* (6. U5 \(input ports 9-12\) interrupt moved from GPIO26 to GPIO32) Tj
T* (7. U7 \(input ports 17-20\) interrupt moved from GPIO4 to GPIO5) Tj
T* (8. U8 \(input ports 21-24\) interrupt moved from GPIO5 to GPIO18) Tj
T* (9. U9 \(input ports 25-28\) interrupt moved from GPIO18 to GPIO19) Tj
T* (10. U10 \(input ports 29-32\) interrupt moved from GPIO19 to GPIO23) Tj
T* /F1 12 Tf
(11. Removed output power supply 510) Tj
/F4 12 Tf
<03a9> Tj
/F1 12 Tf
( array \(C183868\)) Tj
T* (12. Added individual 470 ) Tj
/F4 12 Tf
<03a9> Tj
/F1 12 Tf
( resistors on 5V PCA9685 outputs \(no longer direct drive\)) Tj
T* (13. Corrected U2 address to 0x41) Tj
T* (14. Changed RJ1-RJ4 to use case ground instead of digital ground on the shield) Tj
T* (15. GPIO4 no longer used for PCA9555 interrupt \(U7\); now unassigned/available) Tj
T* (16. Moved front panel button from GPIO32 to GPIO15) Tj
T* (17. Moved front panel button LED from GPIO33 to GPIO2) Tj
T* (18. Changed U24 \(W5500\) RSTn from being constantly pulled high to being pulled high with 10k ) Tj
/F4 12 Tf
<03a9> Tj
/F1 12 Tf
( resistor and connected to GPIO27) Tj
T* (19. Changed U24 \(W5500\) INTn from being disconnected to being connected to GPIO26) Tj
T* (20. Changed U24 \(W5500\) SCSn from being connected to GND to being pulled high with 10k ) Tj
/F4 12 Tf
<03a9> Tj
/F1 12 Tf
( resistor and connected to GPIO25) Tj
T* (21. Improved power conditioning for Ethernet: added LC filter and bulk/decoupling caps on W5500 3.3V analog rail) Tj
T* (22. Corrected MCU \(U11\) from ESP32-WROVER-E-N4R8 \(C967023\) to ESP32-WROVER-E-N16R8 \(C529589\)) Tj
T* (23. Removed 9VDC power system; System will use 12VDC for all client and relay outputs directly from the external power supply) Tj
